{
  "id": "adv_event_2407_02_01",
  "title": "プロローグ",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2407_02_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2407_02_01-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "橋本さんの提案で、星見プロからみんなに\n誕生日プレゼントとして慰安旅行を計画したんだ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Based on Hashimoto-san's suggestion‚ Hoshimi Pro planned\na recreational trip as a birthday present for everyone.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 0.8,
      "endTime": 7.5045124055,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2407_02_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2407_02_01-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "旅行先は俺の方で考えようと思っているけれど\nもし、希望があったら受け付けるよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I'm thinking of deciding the destination myself‚\nbut if you have any requests‚ let me know.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 7.7078681946,
      "endTime": 13.599568748400001,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2407_02_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2407_02_01-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "グループは誕生日が近い人達で組ませてもらったが……\n日頃の疲れを存分に癒して来てくれ！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I grouped people whose birthdays are close together…\nSo‚ please relax and recover from your daily fatigue!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 13.9023346901,
      "endTime": 20.3931735039,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2407_02_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2407_02_01-ngs001.m4a",
      "text": "え？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Eh?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 20.6040805817,
      "endTime": 21.1898818981,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2407_02_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2407_02_01-aoi001.m4a",
      "text": "え？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Eh?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 21.2976602852,
      "endTime": 22.0217664667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2407_02_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2407_02_01-rio001.m4a",
      "text": "ええ？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Eeh?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 22.1040758132,
      "endTime": 23.151513481000002,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "speakerNameEn": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2407_02_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2407_02_01-kor001.m4a",
      "text": "はあ？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Huh?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 23.037408765,
      "endTime": 24.054755743199998,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2407_02_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2407_02_01-mei001.m4a",
      "text": "わーい！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yay!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 24.070742607,
      "endTime": 26.3040779749,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "speakerNameEn": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "――星見プロ誕生日慰安旅行in沖縄",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Hoshimi Pro Birthday Recreational Trip in Okinawa",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 27.1707422891,
      "endTime": 28.8374113717,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_coast-01.m4a",
          "delay": 1833.3388647999982
        },
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_run-coast-single-01.m4a",
          "delay": 2133.335685799999
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_okinawabeach-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "okinawabeach-00-noon",
      "startTime": 28.9374113082
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2407_02_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2407_02_01-mei002.m4a",
      "text": "わーい、海だー！　ねーねー早くみんなで遊びに\n行こうよ！　あ、見て見て！　あっちに屋台も出てる！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yay‚ it's the ocean! Hey‚ hey‚ let's all go play\nLet's go! Oh‚ look‚ look! There are food stalls over there!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 29.870744705,
      "endTime": 39.786547469999995,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-coast-single-01.m4a",
          "delay": 10169.051059300004
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_okinawabeach-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "okinawabeach-00-noon",
      "startTime": 39.9707429248
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2407_02_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2407_02_01-ngs002.m4a",
      "text": "あ、芽衣ちゃん！　{user}さんが\nチェックイン終わるまでもう少しここで待ってよ？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Ah‚ Mei-chan! {user}-san is\nstill checking in‚ so let's wait here a little longer?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 39.9707429248,
      "endTime": 46.4791331607,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_okinawabeach-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "okinawabeach-00-noon",
      "startTime": 46.6707429248
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2407_02_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2407_02_01-rio002.m4a",
      "text": "まさか{user}さんも付いてくるなんてね\nてっきり私達だけで行くのかと思ってたわ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I didn't expect {user}-san would come with us too.\nI totally thought it would just be us going.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 46.6707429248,
      "endTime": 55.100538953,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_okinawabeach-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "okinawabeach-00-noon",
      "startTime": 55.3040762582
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "speakerNameEn": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2407_02_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2407_02_01-kor002.m4a",
      "text": "私達の誕生日は口実で、単に彼が\n休みたかっただけなんじゃない？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Maybe our birthdays were just an excuse‚ and\nhe simply wanted a break‚ don't you think?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 55.3040762582,
      "endTime": 60.9939163842,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_okinawabeach-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "okinawabeach-00-noon",
      "startTime": 61.2040749866
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2407_02_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2407_02_01-mei003.m4a",
      "text": "芽衣は{user}さんも一緒に来てくれて\n嬉しいけどなー。人数多い方が楽しいもん！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "But‚ Mei is happy that {user}-san came too.\nIt's more fun with more people!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 61.2040749866,
      "endTime": 68.11747639960001,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2407_02_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2407_02_01-ngs003.m4a",
      "text": "本当はさとみさんが付いてくるはずだったんですけど\n楽しみにし過ぎて前日に熱を出しちゃったらしくて……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Actually‚ Satomi-san was supposed to come with us‚\nbut it seems she got so excited that she got a fever the day before…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 68.3040749866,
      "endTime": 77.4873595553,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_okinawabeach-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "okinawabeach-00-noon",
      "startTime": 77.6707380929
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2407_02_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2407_02_01-aoi002.m4a",
      "text": "可哀そうだけど、なんだかさとみらしいね\n次の機会があれば一緒に来られるといいな",
      "translations": {
        "en": "That's too bad‚ but somehow it feels like Satomi.\nI hope she can come with us if there's another chance.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 77.6707380929,
      "endTime": 84.5439807573,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_okinawabeach-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "okinawabeach-00-noon",
      "startTime": 84.7374047595
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "speakerNameEn": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2407_02_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2407_02_01-kor003.m4a",
      "text": "はぁ……次なんてないわよ。なんで毎年あなた達と\n旅行になんて行かなきゃいけないのよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Hah… There won't be a next time. Why do I have to\ngo on trips with you guys every year?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 84.7374047595,
      "endTime": 92.356951459,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_okinawabeach-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "okinawabeach-00-noon",
      "startTime": 92.5707380929
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2407_02_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2407_02_01-aoi003.m4a",
      "text": "そんなこと言ってるけど{user}君に\n「旅行先は沖縄がいい」って言ったのは君じゃないか",
      "translations": {
        "en": "You say that‚ but weren't you the one\nwho told {user}-kun \"I want the trip to be in Okinawa‚\" right?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 92.5707380929,
      "endTime": 99.8823705354,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "speakerNameEn": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2407_02_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2407_02_01-kor004.m4a",
      "text": "どーせ断ったって強制的に参加させられるんだから\n自分の希望を言うくらい構わないでしょ？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Even if I refused‚ I'd be forced to participate anyway.\nSo it's fine if I at least state my preference‚ right?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 100.0707380929,
      "endTime": 106.5556812921,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_okinawabeach-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "okinawabeach-00-noon",
      "startTime": 106.7707380929
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2407_02_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2407_02_01-rio003.m4a",
      "text": "うちの事務所が強制参加させることはないと思うわよ\n行きたくないなら欠席でも良かったんじゃない？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I don't think our agency would ever force anyone to participate.\nIf you didn't want to go‚ wouldn't it have been fine to just skip it?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 106.7707380929,
      "endTime": 114.1133444467,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_okinawabeach-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "okinawabeach-00-noon",
      "startTime": 114.3040699003
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "speakerNameEn": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2407_02_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2407_02_01-kor005.m4a",
      "text": "ちょ、うるさいわね！　福利厚生を受けないと損だと\n思っただけよ！　以上！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Hey‚ shut up! I just thought it would be a waste if I don't take advantage\nof the welfare benefits! That's all!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 114.3040699003,
      "endTime": 120.2077886579,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_okinawabeach-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "okinawabeach-00-noon",
      "startTime": 120.4040699003
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2407_02_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2407_02_01-ngs004.m4a",
      "text": "franさん……飛行機の隣の席で\n凄く楽しそうに沖縄の観光雑誌を見てたような～……？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Fran-san… You seemed really happy looking at\nan Okinawa tourist magazine next to me on the plane~…?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 120.4040699003,
      "endTime": 129.6096332548,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2407_02_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2407_02_01-mei004.m4a",
      "text": "昨日、kanaちゃんのSNSでも「浮足立ちの\nfranちゃん」って写真付きの投稿見たような……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yesterday‚ on Kana-chan's SNS‚ I think I saw a post\nwith a picture titled \"Fran-chan all excited\"…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 129.8040780383,
      "endTime": 137.85432217890002,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_okinawabeach-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "okinawabeach-00-noon",
      "startTime": 138.0707396188
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2407_02_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2407_02_01-aoi004.m4a",
      "text": "なんだ、franにも可愛いところがあるじゃないか",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Oh‚ fran has cute sides too.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 138.0707396188,
      "endTime": 142.05003658919998,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_okinawabeach-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "okinawabeach-00-noon",
      "startTime": 142.2374062854
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "speakerNameEn": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2407_02_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2407_02_01-kor006.m4a",
      "text": "あーもう！　別にいいでしょ！　あんた達はあんた達で\n楽しみなさい！　私も一人で勝手に楽しむから。じゃあ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Aah‚ jeez! Whatever! You guys enjoy yourselves!\nI'm going to enjoy myself on my own. See ya.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 142.2374062854,
      "endTime": 150.70407962800002,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_okinawabeach-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "okinawabeach-00-noon",
      "startTime": 150.9374113717
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2407_02_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2407_02_01-mei005.m4a",
      "text": "えぇー！　franちゃんだけ別行動するの……？\nせっかくみんなで来たんだからみんなで遊ぼうよ！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Ehー! Fran-chan‚ are you going to act separately…?\nWe came all this way together‚ so let's all hang out together!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 150.9374113717,
      "endTime": 158.12293183,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_okinawabeach-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "okinawabeach-00-noon",
      "startTime": 154.3374190648
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_okinawabeach-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "okinawabeach-00-noon",
      "startTime": 158.3374215442
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
