      "text": "一応会社のお金で来てるんだし。私達と一緒に\n居たら色々と経費で落ちるかもしれないわね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Well‚ we're here on company money. So‚ if you're with us‚\nvarious things might be covered as expenses‚ you know.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 158.3374215442,
      "endTime": 165.8569907504,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_okinawabeach-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "okinawabeach-00-noon",
